        <div class="c-agi-teaser align-tiles-imagetoLeft teaser--50-50" aria-label="面對石油巨頭，應致力盡職治理而非單純撤資" data-track-info='{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;TeaserTile&quot;,&quot;interaction&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;bannerName&quot;:&quot;面對石油巨頭，應致力盡職治理而非單純撤資&quot;}'>

                <div class="c-agi-teaser__image t-bg-vibrant-cyan-lightest" tabindex="0">
                        <a href="/zh-tw/insights/market-insight/20211120-1-investment-perspective" aria-label="了解更多" data-track="teaserClick" data-track-info='{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;TeaserTile&quot;,&quot;interaction&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;bannerName&quot;:&quot;面對石油巨頭，應致力盡職治理而非單純撤資&quot;}'>
                            <figure class="c-image c-image--1dot8by1">
                                <img src="/-/media/allianzgi/ap/taiwan/insights/weekly-report-tw/2021-11-18-3.png?rev=271cff7d3c5542748444331331fde465&amp;h=1296&amp;w=2304&amp;la=zh-TW&amp;hash=B11CD8E9F5C74BD5DFF266A9F31FA5E5" class="c-image__img" alt="【股市資金觀測】美股資金進補 美中貿易談判正向" />
                            </figure>
                        </a>
                </div>
            <div class="c-agi-teaser__content" tabindex="0">
                <div class="c-agi-tile t-bg-vibrant-cyan-lightest">
                    <div class="c-agi-tile__wrapper">
                        <div class="c-agi-tile__content">
                            <p class="c-copy c-agi-tile__tags">
                                
                            </p>
                            <h4 class="c-heading c-agi-tile__headline c-heading--link-black">
                                面對石油巨頭，應致力盡職治理而非單純撤資
                            </h4>
                            <p class="c-copy c-agi-tile__text">
                                <p>投資人若想確保石油巨頭成為全球在2050年前實現淨零碳排的推動者，最好的做法是致力於集體協同性的互動及參與治理行動。世界迫切需要擴大潔淨能源的來源，而我們認為從石油巨頭撤資對此沒有太大幫助。</p>
                            </p>
                                        <a class="c-link c-link--block c-link--icon" href="/zh-tw/insights/market-insight/20211120-1-investment-perspective" target="_blank"
                                           aria-label="了解更多" data-track="teaserClick" data-track-info='{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;TeaserTile&quot;,&quot;interaction&quot;:&quot;click&quot;,&quot;bannerName&quot;:&quot;面對石油巨頭，應致力盡職治理而非單純撤資&quot;}'>
