        <div class="c-agi-teaser align-tiles-imagetoLeft teaser--50-50" aria-label="碗盤裡的危機：從糧食系統缺失發掘潛在投資契機" data-track-info='{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;TeaserTile&quot;,&quot;interaction&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;bannerName&quot;:&quot;碗盤裡的危機：從糧食系統缺失發掘潛在投資契機&quot;}'>

